                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>Ṣalota ʻEtān</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወእምዝ፡ ይበል፡ እግዚኦ፡ መሐረነ፡ እግዚኦ፡ መሐረነ፡ እግዚኦ፡ መሐረነ። ወይበል፡ ስቡሕ፡ ወውዱስ፡ ዘሣረረ፡ ኵሎ፡ ዓለመ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ቃል።
                     </incipit>
                     <note>	
                        Arranged for the days of the week</note>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">Colophon with date, fol. 94r</colophon>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
